    # "They were all back."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_d56f1dd6 (line 43852)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_d56f1dd6:
    # "And Sarah turned down her eyes and saw her fist clenched around the hilt of her sword."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_ea6576c3 (line 43853)
