    # "Then, looking down, she found the place."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_80c67648 (line 43858)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_80c67648:
    # "Amidst the desert, it seemed the same as any other. To her soul, it seemed unlike any other. This was the space."
