    # "Her soldiers, gathered up a few hundred, beyond the ridge thousands more."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_d3aea9ea (line 43861)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_d3aea9ea:
    # "They looked at her, those blessed few, as though she had gone mad, and they feared seeing their beloved commander lost to madness. For if she could break, how did they stand any chance?"
