# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_1831ec29 (line 43862)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_1831ec29:
    # "Sarah raised her sword up to the sky, gathering their eyes upon her."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_c45afa56 (line 43863)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_c45afa56:
    # "And they did."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_a6da7420 (line 43864)
