    # "They bore witness."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_2da7d792 (line 43865)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_2da7d792:
    # "Seizing the hilt of her blade with two hands, Sarah plunged it with all the force left in her broken body, and drove the blade near half into the earth."
