# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_1331d325 (line 43867)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_1331d325:
    # "But then..."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_96a2a7c2 (line 43868)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_96a2a7c2:
    # "A miracle."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_65748f69 (line 43869)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_65748f69:
    # "First she heared the rushing sound, coming up from deep below the earth."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_90d85a07 (line 43870)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_90d85a07:
    # "Then, the very earth beneath her feet began to twist and move."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e5a1225f (line 43871)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e5a1225f:
    # "And it broke."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_c63643ad (line 43878)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_c63643ad:
    # "Spewing forth from the shattering of the earth, geysers of water, rushing up to meet her."
