# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_2a5df5a4 (line 43880)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_2a5df5a4:
    # "As the torrent of water grew and grew around her, it began to swirl and stream in every direction."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_4e4fc7d9 (line 43881)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_4e4fc7d9:
    # "It flowed past her body, into her armor, spreading out its incomparable relief across her body."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e318d8f7 (line 43882)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e318d8f7:
    # "As Sarah turned up her face to watch the men, she could see that their faces changed."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_21ee1e27 (line 43883)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_21ee1e27:
    # "Respect had given way to worship."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_1a27c8e6 (line 43884)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_1a27c8e6:
    # "For she had given them something nearer to their hearts than anything. Water."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_fee4c590 (line 43885)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_fee4c590:
    # "As their stunned and worshipping faces gave way to the reality of this blessing, the men began to rush forward, down the hill."
