# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_d4867bc4 (line 43886)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_d4867bc4:
    # "They reached for the water in a manic frenzy, as though fearing it might not be real, but their hands and thirsty mouths confirmed that it was."
