# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_3cceb829 (line 43887)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_3cceb829:
    # "With cupped hands they poured the water past their cracked lips and down their tormented throats."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_f1e1e97e (line 43888)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_f1e1e97e:
    # "Behind the first of the men, the news spread like a fever, and soon the rest of the army rushed across the hill and down it to bear witness and bathe in the water."
