# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e01b0bec (line 43890)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e01b0bec:
    # "Deep enough for a man to dissapear into entirely."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_311df991 (line 43891)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_311df991:
    # "So sweet was the relief."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_618d89f4 (line 43892)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_618d89f4:
    # "Touching was not enough."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_118ab3bb (line 43893)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_118ab3bb:
    # "Drinking was not enough."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_56aca080 (line 43894)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_56aca080:
    # "The men of the march began to throw away their weapons and their armors."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_3a2d548b (line 43895)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_3a2d548b:
    # "They needed to feel the water on every facet of their bodies, and so each of them, man or woman, abandoned all sense of shame and leapt into the water naked."
