# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_b4714c81 (line 43901)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_b4714c81:
    # "Casting away her armor onto the shoals, Sarah eagerly stripped everything that stood between herself and her body."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_83b54da4 (line 43902)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_83b54da4:
    # "When she reached down and slipped off the last of her underwear, she could see she was not a sight to behold, but rather one of many."
