# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e77ffab0 (line 43914)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e77ffab0:
    # "Sarah fell back into the water, arms stretched, and staring up into the sky, she doubted how such a thing could be, even as she lived it."
