    # "Drifting, she slowly felt the last of her weariness fade."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_ad8e91e9 (line 43916)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_ad8e91e9:
    # "The water, so perfect in temperature, slowly ebbed away at the edges of her body."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_6501219f (line 43917)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_6501219f:
    # "Where did her body end and the water began?"
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_20609b48 (line 43918)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_20609b48:
    # "With her eyes closed, Sarah could not be sure and she did not want to be sure."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_117915f7 (line 43919)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_117915f7:
    # "Dream."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_75f1b550 (line 43920)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_75f1b550:
    # "Just for a moment."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_ed2e30c1 (line 43921)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_ed2e30c1:
    # "When Sarah opened her eyes again, she wasn't sure how much time had passed."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e3e6ca8d (line 43931)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_e3e6ca8d:
    # "Slowly, Sarah began to swim and carried herself up to the edges of the lake."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_f7f37e39 (line 43932)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_f7f37e39:
    # "The warm sand that had once been such a torture, now felt comfortable on her healed feet."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_7933c373 (line 43933)
