    # "She smiled as she looked around."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_92261d1e (line 43934)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_92261d1e:
    # "The wind ran past her naked and still wet body, but it was gentle."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_f055ec12 (line 43935)
