# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_dee1704b (line 43936)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_dee1704b:
    # "And there was an innocence here, despite everything."
    ""

# TheHollowWorldWarrior6_8df1fb3d (line 43937)
translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior6_8df1fb3d:
    # "Sarah looked around the edges of the water."
    ""

